## PRE-REQUISITE: Splunk HEC Setup (5 min)

Do this **once** before any Terraform:

```
1. Login to Splunk UI
2. Settings → Data Inputs → HTTP Event Collector
3. Click "Global Settings" → Enable Token = ON → Save
4. Click "New Token"
   → Name:       azure-fluentbit
   → Index:      Create two indexes:
                 - vm-logs
                 - aks-logs
5. Save → Copy the token
6. Note: https://<splunk-host>:8088/services/collector
```

