## Deployment Steps (Exact Order)

```bash
# 1. Initialize
terraform init

# 2. Plan — review changes
terraform plan -out=tfplan

# 3. Apply
terraform apply tfplan

# 4. Verify Windows VMs
# Check extension status in Azure Portal:
# VM → Extensions + applications → fluentbit-windows = Succeeded

# 5. Verify Linux/RHEL VMs
# SSH into VM:
sudo systemctl status fluent-bit
sudo journalctl -u fluent-bit -f

# 6. Verify AKS DaemonSet
kubectl get ds -n logging fluent-bit
kubectl get pods -n logging -o wide
kubectl logs -n logging -l app.kubernetes.io/name=fluent-bit --tail=50

# 7. Verify in Splunk
# index=vm-logs  → Windows + Linux logs
# index=aks-logs → container logs
```

