## Key Differences Summary

| | **Linux/RHEL VM** | **Windows VM** | **AKS** |
|--|--|--|--|
| **Method** | Azure VM Extension | Azure VM Extension | Helm DaemonSet |
| **Publisher** | `Microsoft.Azure.Extensions` | `Microsoft.Compute` | N/A |
| **Type** | `CustomScript` | `CustomScriptExtension` | N/A |
| **Version** | `2.1` | `1.10` | chart `0.46.7` |
| **Install** | `yum install fluent-bit` | `.zip` + Windows Service | auto via Helm |
| **Config** | `/etc/fluent-bit/` | `C:\fluent-bit\` | Helm ConfigMap |
| **Log source** | `/var/log/siem/*.log` + systemd | `C:\logs\` + WinLog | `/var/log/containers/` |

